

    <style>
        body {
            
            
            background-color: #2C3D4E;
            
           
            
            
        }

        .container {
            width: 1300px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

            .container .card {
                position: relative;
                cursor: pointer;
                background-color: #2C3D4E;
                border: none;
            }

            

                .container .card .face {
                    width: 300px;
                    height: 200px;
                    transition: 0.5s;
                }

                    .container .card .face.face1 {
                        position: relative;
                        background: #2C3D4E;
                        display: flex;
                        justify-content: center;
                        align-items: center;
                        z-index: 1;
                        transform: translateY(100px);
                    }

                .container .card:hover .face.face1 {
                    background: #D74833;
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }

                .container .card .face.face1 .content {
                    opacity: 0.2;
                    transition: 0.5s;
                }

                .container .card:hover .face.face1 .content {
                    opacity: 1;
                }

                .container .card .face.face1 .content img {
                    max-width: 100px;
                }

                .container .card .face.face1 .content h3 {
                    margin: 10px 0 0;
                    padding: 0;
                    color: #fff;
                    text-align: center;
                    font-size: 1.5em;
                }

                .container .card .face.face2 {
                    position: relative;
                    background: #fff;
                    display: flex;
                    justify-content: center;
                    align-items: center;
                    padding: 20px;
                    box-sizing: border-box;
                    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
                    transform: translateY(-100px);
                }

                .container .card:hover .face.face2 {
                    transform: translateY(0);
                }

                .container .card .face.face2 .content p {
                    font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive, sans-serif;
                    margin: 0;
                    margin-bottom: 20px;
                    padding: 0;
                }

                .container .card .face.face2 .content a {
                    
                    display: inline-block;
                    text-decoration: none;
                    font-weight: 900;
                    color: #333;
                    padding: 5px;
                    border: 1px solid #333;
                }

                    .container .card .face.face2 .content a:hover {
                        background: #333;
                        color: #fff;
                    }

        .container>a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
    </style>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a asp-controller="Map" asp-action="Map">
            <div class="card" style="margin-left: -50px; margin-top: 150px;">
                <div class="face face1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <img src="https://cdn0.iconfinder.com/data/icons/maps-navigation-1/256/15-512.png" />
                        <h3>Places</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="face face2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <p>To win in the marketplace you must first win in the workplace.</p>
                        @*<a href="#">Explore More</a>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a asp-controller="Task" asp-action="AllTasks">
            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 150px;">
                <div class="face face1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <img src="https://www.freeiconspng.com/uploads/tasks-icon-15.png" />
                        <h3>Tasks</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="face face2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <p>If a task is ones begun, never leave it until it's done.</p>
                        @*<a href="#">Explore More</a>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a asp-controller="Meditation" asp-action="MeditationTime">
            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 150px;">
                <div class="face face1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <img src="https://freepngimg.com/download/meditation/7-2-meditation-transparent.png"
                             style="margin-left: 15px" />
                        <h3>Meditation</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="face face2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <p>
                            Briliant things can happen in calm minds. Be calm. You are
                            brilliant.
                        </p>
                        @*<a href="#">Explore More</a>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
        <a asp-controller="Statistics" asp-action="MeditationInfo">
            <div class="card" style="margin-top: 150px;">
                <div class="face face1">
                    <div class="content">
                        <img style="margin-left: 10px"
                             src="https://library.kissclipart.com/20181005/wqe/kissclipart-statistics-vector-png-clipart-statistics-clip-art-c72889d228d98cc8.png" />
                        <h3>Statistics</h3>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="face face2">
                    <div class="content">
                        <p>
                            There are two kinds of statistics, the kind you look up and the kind
                            you make up.
                        </p>
                        @*<a href="#">Explore More</a>*@
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>




